  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401070/extras/30f40ee130c34e22e2e7d7ec2420438d.poster.avif?t=1686832616\" width=498 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401070/extras/30f40ee130c34e22e2e7d7ec2420438d.webm?t=1686832616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401070/extras/30f40ee130c34e22e2e7d7ec2420438d.mp4?t=1686832616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Aim and shoot magic cubes into 3D structures to pop cubes of the same color. <br><br>Find the most effective way to solve the puzzle and earn three stars in each level.<br><br>You have unlimited time, but only a limited amount of spells!<br><br>You'll face very tricky levels, don't be fooled by the easy start...<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Relaxing seated VR gameplay<br></li><li> 165 levels with growing difficulty and boss levels<br></li><li> Steam achievements<br></li><li> Seven beautiful environments<br></li><li> Special cubes with fun mechanics, e.g. <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Bomb – removes all cubes in the explosion radius<br></li><li> Lightning bolt – removes all cubes in one direction<br></li><li> Slime cube – will spread slime to neighboring cubes<br></li><li> …and many more!</li></ul></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401070/extras/30f40ee130c34e22e2e7d7ec2420438d.poster.avif?t=1686832616\" width=498 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401070/extras/30f40ee130c34e22e2e7d7ec2420438d.webm?t=1686832616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401070/extras/30f40ee130c34e22e2e7d7ec2420438d.mp4?t=1686832616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Aim and shoot magic cubes into 3D structures to pop cubes of the same color. <br><br>Find the most effective way to solve the puzzle and earn three stars in each level.<br><br>You have unlimited time, but only a limited amount of spells!<br><br>You'll face very tricky levels, don't be fooled by the easy start...<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Relaxing seated VR gameplay<br></li><li> 165 levels with growing difficulty and boss levels<br></li><li> Steam achievements<br></li><li> Seven beautiful environments<br></li><li> Special cubes with fun mechanics, e.g. <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Bomb – removes all cubes in the explosion radius<br></li><li> Lightning bolt – removes all cubes in one direction<br></li><li> Slime cube – will spread slime to neighboring cubes<br></li><li> …and many more!</li></ul></li></ul>",
